</span></u></span></span><span md-inline="plain" class="md-plain">, que permite adição/alteração/exclusão de filmes e adição/alteração/exclusão de sessões</span></font></p></li></ul><p cid="n60" mdtype="paragraph" class="md-end-block md-p" style="line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0.8em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" open="" sans",="" "clear="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 15px;="" font-weight:="" 400;"=""><span md-inline="strong" class="md-pair-s"><font size="3">Dica:</font></span></p><ul class="ul-list" cid="n61" mdtype="list" data-mark="*" style="margin: 0.8em 0px; padding-left: 30px; position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" open="" sans",="" "clear="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 15px;="" font-weight:="" 400;"=""><li class="md-list-item" cid="n63" mdtype="list_item" style="margin: 0px; position: relative;"><p cid="n64" mdtype="paragraph" class="md-end-block md-p" style="line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;"><span md-inline="plain" class="md-plain"><font size="3">perfis e usuários terão agora um relacionamento n: n</font></span></p></li></ul><p cid="n68" mdtype="paragraph" class="md-end-block md-p" style="line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0.8em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" open="" sans",="" "clear="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 15px;="" font-weight:="" 400;"=""><span md-inline="strong" class="md-pair-s "><font size="3">Exigência:</font></span></p><ul class="ul-list" cid="n72" mdtype="list" data-mark="*" style="margin: 0.8em 0px; padding-left: 30px; position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" open="" sans",="" "clear="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 15px;="" font-weight:="" 400;"=""><li class="md-list-item" cid="n75" mdtype="list_item" style="margin: 0px; position: relative;"><p cid="n76" mdtype="paragraph" class="md-end-block md-p" style="line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative;"><span md-inline="plain" class="md-plain"><font size="3">Implemente esta nova funcionalidade usando SQLAlchemy adotando o relacionamento n:n</font></span></p></li></ul><p cid="n13" mdtype="paragraph" class="md-end-block md-p" style="line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0.8em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" open="" sans",="" "clear="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 15px;="" font-weight:="" 400;"=""><font size="3"><span md-inline="strong" class="md-pair-s ">Valor:</span><span md-inline="plain" class="md-plain"> 2</span></font></p><p cid="n14" mdtype="paragraph" class="md-end-block md-p" style="line-height: inherit; orphans: 4; margin-top: 0.8em; margin-bottom: 0.8em; white-space: pre-wrap; position: relative; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);" open="" sans",="" "clear="" "helvetica="" neue",="" helvetica,="" arial,="" sans-serif;="" font-size:="" 15px;="" font-weight:="" 400;"=""><font size="3"><span md-inline="strong" class="md-pair-s ">Prazo:</span><span md-inline="plain" class="md-plain"> 28/07</span></font></p></h2>', 2, 102, 2, '2021-07-28 23:59:00', false, true);
